00:19:43.360 --> 00:19:44.771
That was embarrassing.

00:19:44.771 --> 00:19:46.270
And I thought about
Bill, and I said

00:19:46.270 --> 00:19:47.590
Bill, do you know about this.

00:19:47.590 --> 00:19:51.100
And he said, yes, sir I did.

00:19:51.100 --> 00:19:52.750
Really?

