Why did you order it?

00:19:55.990 --> 00:19:57.545
What do you guys think he said?

00:19:57.545 --> 00:19:59.920
Exactly, because it's all
about telling people what to do

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:02.800
and doing what you're told.

00:20:02.800 --> 00:20:05.050
And this was like a
hammer blow to my head.

00:20:05.050 --> 00:20:06.550
Because my whole
leadership training

00:20:06.550 --> 00:20:10.030
