And they were like, OK.

00:20:21.017 --> 00:20:22.600
No one knew what
that would look like,

00:20:22.600 --> 00:20:24.610
but it was better than
dying, which is what

00:20:24.610 --> 00:20:26.320
would have happened eventually.

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:29.800
So we say, good leaders give
good orders, that's the myth.

00:20:29.800 --> 00:20:32.050
I now think good leaders
actually don't give orders.

00:20:32.050 --> 00:20:36.516
They create a team that doesn't
need to be told what to do.

00:20:36.516 --> 00:20:38.890
So now I've decided not to
give my guys any instructions.

00:20:38.890 --> 00:20:40.265
I still don't know
the submarine.

00:20:40.265 --> 00:20:43.600
So now I'm a know
not, tell not leader.

