maybe this is where you need
to live for a few days, weeks,

00:20:48.810 --> 00:20:49.310
or months.

00:20:49.310 --> 00:20:50.500
But eventually people
are going to stop

00:20:50.500 --> 00:20:52.110
paying you for being down here.

00:20:52.110 --> 00:20:54.950
So it's not a good
long term strategy.

00:20:54.950 --> 00:20:57.617
Now the torpedoes,
here's how they work.

