00:21:00.450 --> 00:21:03.970
So when we shoot the torpedo, it
connects back to the submarine

00:21:03.970 --> 00:21:05.680
and it sends signals
back saying, here's

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:08.860
what I'm seeing as I'm out
here looking for the bad guy.

