We can chase down the enemy.

00:21:18.349 --> 00:21:19.390
So they're pretty potent.

00:21:19.390 --> 00:21:22.810
Then they don't hit the ship
like you see in the movies.

00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:26.510
They actually go under,
and then they detonate.

00:21:26.510 --> 00:21:29.480
And what we're doing is
blowing a hole in the ocean.

00:21:29.480 --> 00:21:30.070
Why?

00:21:30.070 --> 00:21:33.250
Because then the ship
falls into that hole.

00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:34.030
Breaks in half.

00:21:36.850 --> 00:21:39.760
And you end up right here.

00:21:39.760 --> 00:21:41.290
So that's what sinks the ship.

00:21:41.290 --> 00:21:44.590
So these torpedoes
are big deals.

00:21:44.590 --> 00:21:47.380
Here, we're loading
a torpedo in Japan.

00:21:47.380 --> 00:21:49.510
Now I was all about
empowering my team.

