00:36:52.180 --> 00:37:00.040
You guys are some of the most
creative, talented, smart

00:37:00.040 --> 00:37:06.250
people on the planet, working
for an amazing organization.

00:37:06.250 --> 00:37:10.750
What I worry about
when I interact with--

00:37:10.750 --> 00:37:13.000
you're young people
to me, sorry--

00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:17.350
young people,
millennials, or coders

00:37:17.350 --> 00:37:19.930
is like, I don't care about
that leadership stuff.

00:37:19.930 --> 00:37:22.870
Because we've associated a
bad word with leadership.

00:37:22.870 --> 00:37:25.390
Because leadership means
telling people what to do.

00:37:25.390 --> 00:37:28.000
We have so much baggage
over leadership.

00:37:28.000 --> 00:37:30.940
So I don't want to be a leader,
I just want to be a coder.

00:37:30.940 --> 00:37:34.450
I just want to do my job.

00:37:34.450 --> 00:37:36.830
The world needs you.

00:37:36.830 --> 00:37:39.110
The world needs
you to be leaders,

00:37:39.110 --> 00:37:41.230
not in the traditional,
so I'm going

00:37:41.230 --> 00:37:43.990
