00:37:46.957 --> 00:37:48.790
I'm going to listen to
the diverse opinions,

00:37:48.790 --> 00:37:51.310
I'm going to encourage
someone to say something.

00:37:51.310 --> 00:37:52.840
I'm going to be
part of making it

00:37:52.840 --> 00:37:56.634
safe to say something
that's different than what

00:37:56.634 --> 00:37:57.550
everybody else thinks.

00:38:00.430 --> 00:38:05.260
So that's my ask of you guys.

00:38:05.260 --> 00:38:07.284
Is don't shy away from that.

00:38:07.284 --> 00:38:09.700
Yeah, you've got to do your
job and you've got to do that.

00:38:09.700 --> 00:38:13.840
But start bringing in
this leadership piece.

00:38:13.840 --> 00:38:16.300
You're all leaders,
and we need it.

00:38:16.300 --> 00:38:18.250
The world needs it,
the planet needs it.

00:38:18.250 --> 00:38:23.729
Problems are too complex, too
hard, too sticky, too thorny.

00:38:23.729 --> 00:38:25.270
If you're not
convinced at this point

00:38:25.270 --> 00:38:26.810
