00:41:38.740 --> 00:41:41.230
do you feel that there are
generational differences as far

00:41:41.230 --> 00:41:45.160
as how the leadership
philosophy should be applied.

00:41:45.160 --> 00:41:46.840
Actually, no.

00:41:46.840 --> 00:41:50.080
I think just like all these
myths there's another myth.

00:41:50.080 --> 00:41:51.940
One of the myths
is millennials are

00:41:51.940 --> 00:41:54.280
different than
everybody else, somehow

00:41:54.280 --> 00:41:58.275
